      "created": 1689582893,
      "updated": 1689583433
    },
    {
      "id": "64b4ff3f5b98c20000f7cc5d",
      "text": "　歓迎している感を出すアイデアを求む [suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1689583424,
      "updated": 1689583482
    },
    {
      "id": "64b508495b98c2000003f9fa",
      "text": "　 一般的なこと",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1689585738,
      "updated": 1689585754
    },
    {
      "id": "64b5085a5b98c2000003f9fb",
      "text": "　 　派手な色使いは下品になりやすい",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1689585754,
      "updated": 1689585785
    },
    {
      "id": "64b508795b98c2000003f9fc",
      "text": "　 　グラデーションやアニメーションは苦手な人もいる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1689585785,
      "updated": 1689585818
    },
    {
      "id": "64b4ff7c5b98c20000f7cc5e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1689583485,
      "updated": 1689583485
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd5e64000000000059f145",
      "text": "個別のパーツの輪郭線が重なって見えて読みづらいが、おま環だろうか[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1776115300,
      "updated": 1776115347
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd6118000000000059f147",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/fe4db696077cde0c0179a48d9c1650ff]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1776115997,
      "updated": 1776115997
    },
    {
      "id": "69dd5e64000000000059f146",
      "text": " ちょっと調べてみます [suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776115300,
      "updated": 1776116178
    },
    {
